snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe Ghum Hai Kisikey Pyaar Meiin : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCh9Ao0KLPNXGsHqvIU1pdVw

Click here to Subscribe Star Plus : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-LPIU24bQXVljUXivKEeRQ


*About* 
------------

       Police officer Virat Chavan ne diya vaada apne marte hue junior ko ke rakhenge woh khayal unki beti, Sai ka. Virat aur Sai bandh gaye anchaahe shaadi ke bandhan mai. Virat ka dil tha Patralekha ke paas jiski shaadi hojati hai kisi aur se. Virat ne vaada kiya Pakhi se ke woh uski jagah kabhi kisi aur ko nahi dega. 
                Virat ne bhale nahi diya Sai ko ek pati ka pyaar par unke rishtey mai izzat hamesha thi. Waqt ke saath saath, Virat ne dekha Sai ka accha roop aur hogaya ussey Sai se pyaar. Yeh kahani hai Virat, Sai aur Patralekha ke pyaar ki.

snippet.title: Joker: Folie À Deux | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
When you’re smiling, the whole world smiles with you. Joker: Folie À Deux – only in theaters and IMAX, October 4. #JokerMovie #FilmedForIMAX 

From acclaimed writer/director/producer Todd Phillips comes “Joker: Folie À Deux,” the much-anticipated follow-up to 2019’s Academy Award-winning “Joker,” which earned more than $1 billion at the global box office and remains the highest-grossing R-rated film of all time.  The new film stars Joaquin Phoenix once again in his Oscar-winning dual role as Arthur Fleck/Joker, opposite Oscar winner Lady Gaga (“A Star Is Born”).

“Joker: Folie À Deux” finds Arthur Fleck institutionalized at Arkham awaiting trial for his crimes as Joker. While struggling with his dual identity, Arthur not only stumbles upon true love, but also finds the music that's always been inside him.

The film also stars Oscar nominees Brendan Gleeson (“The Banshees of Inisherin”) and Catherine Keener (“Get Out,” “Capote”), alongside Zazie Beetz, reprising her role from “Joker.”

Phillips, who was nominated for Oscars for directing, writing and producing “Joker,” directed “Joker: Folie À Deux” from a screenplay by fellow Oscar nominee Scott Silver & Phillips, based on characters from DC.  The film was produced by Phillips, Oscar nominee Emma Tillinger Koskoff and Joseph Garner.  Lady Gaga served as music consultant.  The film’s executive producers are Michael E. Uslan, Georgia Kacandes, Silver, Mark Friedberg and Jason Ruder.

Working with Phillips behind the camera are his team from “Joker,” including Oscar-nominated director of photography Lawrence Sher, production designer Mark Friedberg, Oscar-nominated editor Jeff Groth, and composer Hildur Guđnadóttir, who won the Oscar for her work on the first film.  New to the team is Oscar-nominated costume designer Arianne Phillips (“Once Upon a Time in… Hollywood,” “Don’t Worry Darling”).  Ruder is the film’s executive music producer and the music supervisors are Randall Poster and George Drakoulias.  Casting is by Francine Maisler (the “Dune” films, “Challengers”).

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents A Joint Effort Production, A Film by Todd Phillips, “Joker: Folie À Deux.”  The film will be released worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, and will be only in theaters nationwide on October 4, 2024, and beginning internationally on 2 October, 2024.

snippet.title: एक Skit के Through CID ने हल की Case की Mystery! | CID | सी.आई.डी.| Latest Episode| 23 July 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

A woman's ghost is haunting the city and causing destruction around. The idea of a ghost doesn't fit well with CID. They decide to look into it, follow the trail, and validate their suspicions that a person is behind all of this. Stay tuned in to learn more!

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1101
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #CID2024 #LatestTV #SonySET #SETIndia #LatestFromTV #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Possessed Files' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIUAuhlodjdo4EsBMv_8aT16

Shiddat Episode 49 [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Anmol Baloch - 23rd July 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

Episode 4143: Breakfast For Gokuldham
--------------------------------------------------------
Dr. Hathi and his wife organize a grand special breakfast for the Gokuldham residents. They visit each house to ensure nobody eats before the surprise meal. Will their plans unfold smoothly?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4143 | 22 July 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: गर्मागर्म खस्ता स्वीटकॉर्न पनीर पराठा-मानसून स्पेशल परफेक्ट नाश्ता-Healthy Sweet Corn Paneer Paratha
snippet.description:
बारिश के मौसम का मज़ा लें खस्ता पनीर स्वीट कॉर्न पराठा के साथ, Paneer and Sweet Corn Stuffed Paratha Recipe, Crispy and Soft Paneer Sweet Corn Paratha, Lunchbox Special

#paratha #nashta #sweetcorn #tiffinboxrecipes 

Ingredients for Corn Paneer Paratha
गेहूं का आटा - Wheat flour - 1 cup (150 grams)
बेसन - Gram flour - 2 tbsp
अजवाइन - Carom seeds - 1/4 tsp
कसूरी मेथी - Fenugreek leaves - 1 tbsp
नमक - Salt - 1/3 tsp
घी - Ghee - 1 tsp
स्वीट कॉर्न कौब - Sweet corn cob - 1 no

For Stuffing
तेल - Oil - 2 tsp
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1/4 tsp
अदरक - Ginger - 1 tsp, grated
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1/2 tsp, chopped
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1 tsp
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli - 1/2 tsp
अमचूर पाउडर - Dried mango powder - 1/3 tsp
गरम मसाला - Garam masala - 1/4 tsp
नमक - Salt - 1/3 tsp
शिमला मिर्च - Capsicum - 1/4 cup, chopped
पनीर - Paneer - 1/2 cup, grated
हरा धनिया - Coriander - 2-3 tbsp

snippet.description:
Nachle, main shaukan nachne di!
 
Presenting the hottest party track of the season, Shaukan’ is composed by Shashwat Sachdev, penned by Kumaar and sung by Neha Kakkar, Jubin Nautiyal and Shashwat Sachdev. The first song from the highly awaited film ‘Ulajh’, it’s bound to get you off your feet and dancing!
 
#Shaukan #NehaKakkar #JanhviKapoor #JubinNautiyal #ShashwatSachdev #GulshanDevaiah #RoshanMatthew
 
Composer - Shashwat Sachdev
Singers - Neha Kakkar; Jubin Nautiyal; Shashwat Sachdev
Lyricist - Kumaar
Music Producer - Shashwat Sachdev
Music Production Assistant - Adarsh Vishwakarma
Choreographer: Vijay Ganguly
 
Ulajh releasing in cinemas – 2nd August
 
Presented by: Junglee Pictures
Directed by: Sudhanshu Saria
Produced by: Vineet Jain
Co-produced by: Amrita Pandey
Written by:  Parveez Shaikh & Sudhanshu Saria
Starring – Janhvi Kapoor, Gulshan Devaiah, Roshan Mathew, Meiyang Chang, Rajesh Tailang, Adil Hussain, Jitendra Joshi

Poora galat bana do
Thoda ye dil aawara hai

Daanton se dabe, honthon ke hai kinaare samajh jaiye

Poora galat bana do

Nachle main shaukan nachne di

snippet.title: Kolkata Protest: Student unions stage a protest amid the ongoing anti quota protests in Bangladesh
snippet.description:
Kolkata Protest: 'খুনি হাসিনার শাস্তি চাই', বাংলাদেশ-বিক্ষোভে রণক্ষেত্র বৃষ্টিভেজা কলকাতা। বাংলাদেশের অশান্তির আঁচ তিলোত্তমায়। ওপার বাংলার 'পাশে' একাধিক বামপন্থী ছাত্র সংগঠন।
W.B All India Democratic Students' Organisation (AIDSO) stage a protest amid the ongoing anti-quota protests in Bangladesh. The protestors demand the punishment of Bangladesh Prime Minister Sheikh Hasina.

Jaan Nisar Episode 35 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 21st July 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

snippet.title: विजय राज कौवा बिरयानी कॉमेडी सीन - Vijay Raaz Kauwa Biryani Comedy Scene | Run | Best Hindi Comedy
snippet.description:
Hilarious Kauwa Biryani Comedy Scene of Vijay Raaz from Movie: Run (2004)

Dive into the rib-tickling world of "Run" (2004) with these iconic comedy scenes featuring the legendary Vijay Raaz! This Bollywood gem, directed by Jeeva and produced by Boney Kapoor and Sridevi, showcases Vijay Raaz at his comedic best. Watch as he brings laughter to every frame with his impeccable timing and hilarious antics. Relive the unforgettable "Kauwa Biryani" scene, where Vijay Raaz's character hilariously mistakes crow meat for chicken, delivering the classic line, "Yeh kaunsi biryani hai?" The film stars Abhishek Bachchan and Bhoomika Chawla in the lead roles, with a memorable soundtrack composed by Vidyasagar. Whether you're looking for a hearty laugh or just want to relive some classic comedy moments, these scenes are sure to leave you in splits!

फिल्म रन (2004) से विजय राज के मजेदार कौआ बिरयानी कॉमेडी सीन

"रन" (2004) की दुनिया में विजय राज के इन मशहूर कॉमेडी सीन्स के साथ प्रवेश करें! इस बॉलीवुड रत्न को जीव द्वारा निर्देशित किया गया है और बोनी कपूर और श्रीदेवी द्वारा निर्मित किया गया है। फिल्म में अभिषेक बच्चन और भूमिका चावला मुख्य भूमिकाओं में हैं, और इसका यादगार साउंडट्रैक विद्यसागर द्वारा रचित है। विजय राज अपनी बेमिसाल टाइमिंग और मजेदार हरकतों के साथ हर फ्रेम में हंसी का तड़का लगाते हैं। अविस्मरणीय "कौवा बिरयानी" सीन को फिर से जीएं, जहां विजय राज का किरदार कौवे के मांस को चिकन समझकर मजाकिया अंदाज में पूछता है, "ये कौनसी बिरयानी है?" चाहे आपको जोरदार हंसी चाहिए या बस कुछ क्लासिक कॉमेडी पलों को फिर से जीना चाहते हैं, ये सीन निश्चित रूप से आपको हंसते-हंसते लोटपोट कर देंगे!

Enjoy and share the laughter!

Dive into the rib-tickling world of "Run" (2004) with these iconic comedy scenes featuring the legendary Vijay Raaz! This Bollywood gem, directed by Jeeva and produced by Boney Kapoor and Sridevi, showcases Vijay Raaz at his comedic best. Watch as he brings laughter to every frame with his impeccable timing and hilarious antics. Relive the unforgettable "Kauwa Biryani" scene, where Vijay Raaz's character hilariously mistakes crow meat for chicken, delivering the classic line, "Yeh kaunsi biryani hai?" The film stars Abhishek Bachchan and Bhoomika Chawla in the lead roles, with a memorable soundtrack composed by Vidyasagar. Whether you're looking for a hearty laugh or just want to relive some classic comedy moments, these scenes are sure to leave you in splits!

फिल्म रन (2004) से विजय राज के मजेदार कौआ बिरयानी कॉमेडी सीन

"रन" (2004) की दुनिया में विजय राज के इन मशहूर कॉमेडी सीन्स के साथ प्रवेश करें! इस बॉलीवुड रत्न को जीव द्वारा निर्देशित किया गया है और बोनी कपूर और श्रीदेवी द्वारा निर्मित किया गया है। फिल्म में अभिषेक बच्चन और भूमिका चावला मुख्य भूमिकाओं में हैं, और इसका यादगार साउंडट्रैक विद्यसागर द्वारा रचित है। विजय राज अपनी बेमिसाल टाइमिंग और मजेदार हरकतों के साथ हर फ्रेम में हंसी का तड़का लगाते हैं। अविस्मरणीय "कौवा बिरयानी" सीन को फिर से जीएं, जहां विजय राज का किरदार कौवे के मांस को चिकन समझकर मजाकिया अंदाज में पूछता है, "ये कौनसी बिरयानी है?" चाहे आपको जोरदार हंसी चाहिए या बस कुछ क्लासिक कॉमेडी पलों को फिर से जीना चाहते हैं, ये सीन निश्चित रूप से आपको हंसते-हंसते लोटपोट कर देंगे!

Enjoy and share the laughter!

Movie: Run (2004)
Cast: Vijay Raaz, Abhishek Bachchan, Bhumika Chawla, Mahesh Manjrekar, Mukesh Rishi.
Music: Himesh Reshammiya, Naresh Sharma
Director: Jeeva
Producer: Boney Kapoor, Sridevi, Surinder Kapoor

snippet.title: কারফিউ জারির পরে শনিবার দিনে কী অবস্থা বাংলাদেশে?
snippet.description:
বাংলাদেশে কারফিউ জারি হওয়ার পর সারা দিনের গুরুত্বপূর্ণ সব খবর ঢাকা থেকে জানিয়েছেন বিবিসির সংবাদদাতারা। ইন্টারনেট সেবা সম্পূর্ণ বন্ধ থাকায় সেখান থেকে সরাসরি খবরাখবর পাঠানোর কাজ ব্যহত হচ্ছে। তবে তাদের দেওয়া তথ্য নিয়ে কলকাতা থেকে বিবিসির অমিতাভ ভট্টশালীর এই প্রতিবেদন:

*******************************************
বিবিসি নিউজ বাংলার ইউটিউব চ্যানেলে আপনাকে স্বাগতম। 
এখানে আপনি দেখতে পাবেন দেশ ও দেশের বাইরের সমসাময়িক গুরুত্বপূর্ণ ঘটনাবলী নিয়ে বস্তুনিষ্ঠ ও বিশ্লেষণধর্মী প্রতিবেদন, বিবিসি নিউজ বাংলার টিভি অনুষ্ঠান প্রবাহ এবং বাংলাদেশ ট্রেন্ডিং-এর সকল কন্টেন্ট। নিয়মিত ভিডিও আপডেট পেতে এবং অনুষ্ঠান দেখতে সাবস্ক্রাইব করতে ভুলবেন না!

snippet.title: Madhavi को पता चला Bhide का Secret |Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah|Biwi Ke Pet Mein Baat Nahi Rukti
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to the Sony LIV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv

Mr. Sharma requests that Jethalal and his neighbors share a secret with their spouses to test if they will divulge it to others or not. Jethalal requests that Bagha provide CCTV equipment to the Gokuldham Society. Taarak and his friends share their secrets with their wives.




Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonyliv #comedy #comedy2024 #jethalal #jethalalcomedy 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

#tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah 

Click here to watch episodes from TMKOC: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLn5vww_8o5Ks1Bs2lrVjAd2ZT_iibaq0K

ଦୁଇ ମା'ଙ୍କ ଭିତରେ ଥିବା ଲକ୍ଷ୍ମଣରେଖାକୁ କଣ ପୋଛି ଦେଇ ପାରିବେ ପଲ୍ଲବୀ ଓ ଆଦର୍ଶ !  ଜଣେ ଜନ୍ମ ଦେଇଚି ଆଉ ଜଣେ ପାଳିଚି , କାହା କଥା ଶୁଣିବ ଆଦର୍ଶ ??

snippet.title: On Camera: CJI Chandrachud Angry At Lawyer, Calls Security During SC NEET Hearing | NTA | Paper Leak
snippet.description:
Chief Justice of India DY Chandrachud schooled a lawyer today for attempting to disrupt proceedings during the Supreme Court's hearing on alleged irregularities in the National Eligibility cum Entrance Test (NEET). NEET is a nationwide examination for admission to medical courses. Advocate Mathews Nedumpara, representing one of the petitioners, interrupted while Narender Hooda, also a petitioner's representative, was addressing the bench.
